# whitespace-only-line-at-start

## Input

```
   
key value

```

## CST

```
SOURCE_FILE@0..14
  SPACE@0..3 "   "
  NEWLINE@3..4 "\n"
  ENTRY@4..14
    WORD_KEY@4..7
      WORD@4..7 "key"
    SPACE@7..8 " "
    LINE_STRING@8..13
      STRING@8..13 "value"
    NEWLINE@13..14 "\n"
```

## AST

```
SourceFile {
    shebang: none,
    items: [
        Entry {
            key: WordKey {
                word: WORD@4..7 "key",
            },
            value: LineString {
                string: STRING@8..13 "value",
            },
        },
    ],
}
```

